{"tid":1475696,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"MG《鐵血孤兒》高達巴巴托司　超可動．靚骨架　完美取代HiRM版","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:48:37.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc1165ae3fea0ff64e10577ed257ed254cec1ec","tid":1475696,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"【MG 1/100 Master Grade 高達巴巴托司 Gundam Barbatos】《機動戰士高達 鐵血孤兒》主角機 Gundam Barbatos 設定就像一部古羅馬角鬥士，以人稱「燒豬叉」的鈍器取代光束劍，粗暴兇悍的外型跟過去所有高達主角機都不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n無論作品有多大爭議性，這部出色設計的高達，向來都多fans。所以BANDAI曾於2016年以巴巴托司作為半完成品新系列HiRM模型的頭炮：使用預製可動骨架，用家只需自己組裝外甲即可把玩，可惜當時此系列風格未穩定成熟，皮與骨未能融為一髒，身型線條比例並不好。<br />\n<br />\n相信BANDAI Hobby部也希望精益求精，3年後上製作MG版高達巴巴托司，要講優點就是技術又進步了，內骨的身型更流線修長， 可動性高，基本上可以做足大張正己作畫的動畫版內任何甫士！且外甲也比HiRM的偷得更薄，不再出現骨肉分離、欠缺一體感的慘況，看官圖，無論是戰鬥時的高度奔走行、ending時跪在地上的動作都做得自然。11月已經有得玩，售4950日圓（約＄350）"},{"pid":"2aa008979ea429d0dec35fbbea1bcb57e48eee27","tid":1475696,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"比蓋清水左去睇"},{"pid":"95c93127dd8441a5721aba78881b950fb13f4b7c","tid":1475696,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"有巴力未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f826959b5b0178431c6baacd4f329cb2cd48c94","tid":1475696,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117131/org/4cb48a95f4670ef86800eb8e7eae846e.jpg/dbPKJY5Mp4PkQvw29ZwYOrSLtZ3mAoEaPfO3xz3zt8c?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117131%2Forg%2F4cb48a95f4670ef86800eb8e7eae846e.jpg%2FdbPKJY5Mp4PkQvw29ZwYOrSLtZ3mAoEaPfO3xz3zt8c%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e7de108d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117126/org/645346f167d2b90d0157b28733289dad.jpg/S96i4FcaffPvvtLEuPJMrwsmh62Jvgekon0KUaJ9ClE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"